---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Kitchen Cabinets — Ardmore & the Main Line
description: Cabinets designed in 3D and coordinated with your counters and tile — one shop, one crew, one install date, anywhere in Greater Philadelphia.
permalink: /cabinets/
---

<div class="hero hero--short">
  <div class="hero__copy">
    <span class="kicker">Cabinetry</span>
    <h1>CAD-designed cabinets, built to fit the stone.</h1>
    <p class="lede" style="font-size:16px">We design your cabinets in 3D and coordinate them with your counters and tile — one shop, one crew, one install date.</p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--dark" href="/contact/">Design My Kitchen</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero__media">
    <img src="/assets/img/cabinets-hero.webp" alt="Warm maple kitchen cabinets with glass uppers, granite counters, and a black island">
  </div>
</div>

{# Door-styles grid removed for now (data still in cabinets.json) — cabinet lines take its slot. #}
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>Our cabinet lines</h2>
    <p class="lede lede--sm" style="max-width:44ch">We carry top-rated cabinetry from five makers — every line on display in the Ardmore showroom. Browse a catalog, then come see the doors in person.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid--3 mfr-grid">
    {% for m in manufacturers %}
      <a class="mfr-card" href="{{ m.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="mfr-card__logo"><img src="{{ m.logo }}" alt="{{ m.name }} logo" loading="lazy"></span>
        <span class="card__title">{{ m.name }}</span>
        <span class="card__meta">{{ m.desc }}</span>
        <span class="text-link">View catalog →</span>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<div class="band" style="padding:64px var(--pad-x)">
  <span class="kicker kicker--light">How it works</span>
  <h2 style="margin:12px 0 40px">From measurement to installed in three steps.</h2>
  <div class="grid grid--3" style="gap:40px">
    {% for s in cabinets.steps %}
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step__num">{{ s.num }}</span>
        <h3>{{ s.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ s.desc }}</p>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

{% set cta = { text: "One crew handles cabinets, counters, and tile.", button: "Get a Free Estimate" } %}
{% include "partials/cross-cta.njk" %}
